  "Description": {
    "English": "A living, fertile egg, <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">ready to hatch!</span><br><br>The little embryo is coiled tightly within the egg, dreaming of stretching its long neck in the sun.<br><br>Scans indicate the being within has the genetic potential for a <span class=\"name name-fuel\">territorial</span> nature, making for a powerful and loyal companion.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一枚有生命的、可孵化的卵，<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">已经准备好孵化！</span><br><br>卵里面的小小胚胎紧紧蜷缩成了一团，它梦想着能够在阳光之下伸展自己长长的脖子与尾巴。<br><br>根据扫描结果显示，里面的生物拥有<span class=\"name name-fuel\">领地意识</span>的基因潜质，并且能够成为一位强大而且忠诚的同伴",
    "TraditionalChinese": "有生命的受精卵<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">隨時會孵化！</span><br><br>小胚胎蜷縮在蛋殼內，夢想在陽光下伸展牠的長脖子和尾巴。<br><br>掃描顯示基因可能天生帶有<span class=\"name name-fuel\">領域性</span>，很適合作為強力又忠誠的同伴。"
  },
